    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it still feels like you're dodging the real issue though. you keep saying \"many argue\" or \"proponents view it as,\" but if you actually look at how it plays out in universities or workplaces, it feels more like a set of rigid rules that everyone is forced to follow under threat of being canceled. can't you just say if the current state of things is more about progress or more about control?",
